  "name": "RPlog_A_Pirate_s_Trap",
  "title": "A Pirate's Trap",
  "summary": "Aboard the CSA Star Destroyer Litigator, a joint ESPO and CorSec strike force prepares to raid pirate facilities when Captain Gren Delede's battle-damaged starfighter limps into the hangar -- empty, its terrified astromech SH0RTY bearing a holo-recording that shows Delede stunned and captured during a recon of explosive-laden ghost ships. Chief of Security Wuv, CorSec Colonel Twila Virda, and the embedded reporter Shakir mount a rescue, with Twila bent on saving her captured love and Wuv wary of the orbiting bomb-ships. Their assault shuttle is shot down on approach, killing the crew and many troops, and the survivors fight their way through the White Death pirates' camp and into the mountain bunker, dragging along a cowardly captured Rodian named Dandoi to open the doors. They find Delede tortured and missing an eye; Twila is wounded in the firefight as the white-clad pirate leader escapes with a flash grenade, but SH0RTY shuts down the bomb-ships' transmitters in time to summon the fleet, which arrives to bombard the camp as Delede stumbles to the fallen Twila's side and the rescue is won at a grim cost.",
